<plot>In the spirit of Waiting for Guffman and Spinal Tap , DAS BUS combines real and staged events alongside archival footage as viewers experience "BUS CULTURE" in the "Bible Belt" metropolis of Kansas City. With Guest appearances by crime novelist James Ellroy and rap star Tech N9NE, DAS BUS is a thought provoking romp that will confront everyone's attitude about public transportation. You will laugh, you will cry, you will empathize, you will say "no way"--an independent film in the true sense of the word.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?127799</url></doc>
